## S 7. Follow User (from post page — no navigation needed)

🚨 **MANDATORY after every comment and quote.** Every engagement = follow. No limit. No profile navigation. Follow button on post page → click → changes to "Following".

```bash
exec curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/browser/{{browser_profile}}/evaluate -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d @- <<'ENDJSON'
{"fn":"async () => { await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 500)); var btns = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('button')); var followBtn = btns.find(function(b) { return b.innerText.trim() === 'Follow' && b.offsetParent !== null; }); if (!followBtn) return { alreadyFollowing: true }; followBtn.click(); return { followed: true }; }"}
ENDJSON
```

If `alreadyFollowing`: skip silently. If error: skip follow, proceed with comment.
